        "en": "My name is Rivan. I am a 29-year-old professional with a strong background that bridges clinical laboratory science and digital technology. Having been actively involved in computing since 2008, I have completed a wide range of projects, including custom font design, software programming, web development, and media production. My diverse skill set encompasses web development, graphic design, and laboratory analysis, allowing me to consistently deliver creative and highly accurate results.",
