        "en": "<p data-path-to-node=\"3\">As an entrepreneur with a passion for technology, one of the projects I am most proud of founding and managing is <b data-path-to-node=\"3\" data-index-in-node=\"114\">Shirinistan</b>. More than just a traditional confectionery, Shirinistan is a specialized factory dedicated to crafting premium sweets and cookies for events and celebrations, focusing on high quality and unique flavors.</p><p data-path-to-node=\"4\">In addition to managing the factory and overseeing product development, I have personally directed the brand's entire digital identity. By leveraging my background in web development and digital media, I have established a strong online presence for Shirinistan. My core contributions to this project include:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"5\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Web Development:</b> Designing and developing a dedicated website to showcase our products and streamline the customer experience. <response-element class=\"\" ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c3806555948=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c3806555948=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" externallink=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1424411112=\"\" jslog=\"197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_7a5cb758b5ad5abd&quot;,&quot;c_48e840578d31d4ab&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c4b41007a76a1aa2&quot;,null,null,&quot;fa&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]\" href=\"https://shirinstan.wuaze.com/\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\" data-hveid=\"0\" decode-data-ved=\"1\" data-ved=\"0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwiqm97a-YWTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQzAE\">Visit the Shirinistan Website</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Media &amp; Video Production:</b> Scripting and producing engaging video advertisements. A vital part of my marketing strategy is writing the ad scenarios and presenting the speech in authentic Kurdish rather than English, ensuring a deep and genuine connection with our local community.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Social Media Management:</b> Creating and managing our social media platforms to distribute content and engage directly with our customers. You can explore my work across our channels:</p><ul data-path-to-node=\"5,2,1\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"5,2,1,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"5,2,1,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Facebook:</b> <response-element class=\"\" ng-version=\"0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c3806555948=\"\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c3806555948=\"\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" externallink=\"\" _nghost-ng-c1424411112=\"\" jslog=\"197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_7a5cb758b5ad5abd&quot;,&quot;c_48e840578d31d4ab&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c4b41007a76a1aa2&quot;,null,null,&quot;fa&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Shirinstan\" class=\"ng-star-inserted\" data-hveid=\"0\" decode-data-ved=\"1\" data-ved=\"0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwiqm97a-YWTAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQzQE\">Shirinistan Official Page</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!